Label&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;In the News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;NBCnews.com features the &lt;a href=&quot;https://professionals.collegeboard.org/k-12/all-in&quot;&gt;All In Campaign&lt;/a&gt; in an article about the value of &lt;span&gt;using AP potential to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;expand access to AP for African American, Latino, and Native American students.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
